Authors@R: person("Keon-Woong", "Moon", email = "cardiomoon@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/cardiomoon/dplyrAssist                  
Description: The 'dplyrAssist' is an RStudio addin for teaching and learning
    data manipulation using the 'dplyr' package. You can learn each steps of data
    manipulation by clicking your mouse without coding. You can get resultant
    data(as a 'tibble') and the code for data manipulation.
